1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:01,430
Day 1 ended.

2
00:00:01,430 --> 00:00:03,022
Zero trades.

3
00:00:03,022 --> 00:00:04,358
Zero profit.

4
00:00:04,358 --> 00:00:09,194
And I learned more than 7 days of paper testing ever taught me.

5
00:00:09,194 --> 00:00:10,666
I can't code.

6
00:00:10,666 --> 00:00:12,847
9 years in crypto.

7
00:00:12,847 --> 00:00:17,097
7 days ago I asked AI to build me a trading bot.

8
00:00:17,097 --> 00:00:23,027
I put a thousand down for this experiment — if it works, any ordinary person can use it.

9
00:00:23,027 --> 00:00:26,861
This is Day 1 of AI trading my thousand dollars.

10
00:00:26,861 --> 00:00:30,555
Today it trades with my real money for the first time.

11
00:00:30,555 --> 00:00:35,291
One word in the config — paper to live — real money starts.

12
00:00:35,291 --> 00:00:40,458
I changed it, and stared at the Enter key for 20 minutes.

13
00:00:40,458 --> 00:00:46,152
Then this thought hits me — if this loses everything tonight, how do I tell anyone?

14
00:00:46,152 --> 00:00:50,291
That thought, in paper mode, never once crossed my mind.

15
00:00:50,291 --> 00:00:51,776
Not once.

16
00:00:51,776 --> 00:00:53,236
I pressed.

17
00:00:53,236 --> 00:00:54,763
Nothing happened.

18
00:00:54,763 --> 00:00:56,916
One hour, no trade.

19
00:00:56,916 --> 00:00:59,041
Two hours, still nothing.

20
00:00:59,041 --> 00:01:00,916
It was waiting for a signal.

21
00:01:00,916 --> 00:01:02,527
I was waiting for it.

22
00:01:02,527 --> 00:01:05,180
By hour three my eyes hurt.

23
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:07,388
So I washed dishes.

24
00:01:07,388 --> 00:01:11,347
Halfway through the sink, I realized I'd relaxed.

25
00:01:11,347 --> 00:01:13,111
Something had shifted.

26
00:01:13,111 --> 00:01:15,152
I couldn't have told you what.

27
00:01:15,152 --> 00:01:16,291
Day 1.

28
00:01:16,291 --> 00:01:17,897
Zero trades.

29
00:01:17,897 --> 00:01:21,930
But most of what I learned all week came from those three hours.

30
00:01:21,930 --> 00:01:24,861
Day 2 tomorrow — it actually traded.

31
00:01:24,861 --> 00:01:27,263
Follow if you want to see what happened next.

